&lt;p&gt;GLENT &amp;#8211; is one of the most luxurious beauty salons of the historic center of the capital. It is located in a historic building of the New Arbat and attracts attention with its elegance. Talented designers created here the atmosphere of a magnificent palace.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;42 specialists of GLENT &amp;#8211; are professionals with extensive experience, and there are no unsolvable problems for them. GLENT has the best equipment, uses only the most modern and safest methods of aesthetic and medical cosmetology, as well as cosmetic brands with an impeccable reputation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;European quality of service and customized beauty programs expect you here. Stylists, makeup artists, masters of nail service know all about fashion and more &amp;#8211; they are connoisseurs of beauty and know how to interpret the fashion trends, creating a unique image.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;After opening the second area of the Beauty Salon GLENT became even more like a marvelous palace and offers its guests vip-rooms and new services, like hamam.&lt;/p&gt;
